title: Global markets edgy as investors gauge chances of Federal Reserve rate cut
description: Cavan-based insulation specialist Kingpan climbed 1.5% in Dublin after almost 47m shares were traded
content:
Global shares were mixed on Wednesday even after weak US economic data solidified expectations of a Federal Reserve interest rate cut.
